00:17:59.510 --> 00:17:59.520
Finally, she shouted, 'I told you to get!'and that dog bolted back to the house. That's how you have to talk to the devil. The Bible says in James to submit yourself to God, resist the devil, and he will flee. You have to

00:17:59.520 --> 00:18:01.870
