00:29:18.000 --> 00:29:19.750
used

00:29:19.750 --> 00:29:19.760
my

00:29:19.760 --> 00:29:21.669
authority.

00:29:21.679 --> 00:29:23.950
I could see the clouds

00:29:23.960 --> 00:29:26.110
