00:29:57.830 --> 00:29:57.840
you

00:29:57.840 --> 00:30:00.590
can speak to

00:30:00.600 --> 00:30:03.389
sickness and disease

00:30:03.399 --> 00:30:06.190
yourself.

00:30:06.200 --> 00:30:08.430
I call in high-pressure

00:30:08.430 --> 00:30:08.440
and low-pressure

00:30:08.440 --> 00:30:11.029
