00:31:17.519 --> 00:31:20.029
It takes faith.

00:31:20.039 --> 00:31:21.509
Sometimes I

00:31:21.509 --> 00:31:21.519
call

00:31:21.519 --> 00:31:24.269
for

00:31:24.279 --> 00:31:26.629
