00:32:18.000 --> 00:32:19.710
Speak

00:32:28.399 --> 00:32:30.669
over your finances,

00:32:30.679 --> 00:32:33.669
your health,

00:32:33.669 --> 00:32:33.679
and

00:32:33.679 --> 00:32:35.470
your children.

00:32:35.470 --> 00:32:35.480
Listen

00:32:35.480 --> 00:32:38.389
to that still, small

00:32:38.399 --> 00:32:41.110
voice.

